true
false
This field is automatically populated via a formula. It stores the current LTV of the loan based on its Collateral Mgmt records. If the Product Feature is NOT a Line of Credit, or if the Product Feature does not exist, this is the formula: (Principal Balance + Total Prior Lien Amount from all Collateral)/ Collateral Value from all Collateral. LLC_BI__Overdraft_Consent__c
Overdraft Consent
Picklist
true
false
This picklist field is populated during the deposit account opening process. This field indicates the decision made by the customer to either request or refuse institution overdraft services that include and cover overdraft activity on ATM and everyday debit card transactions as part of standard overdraft services. The statement that reflects the customer's decision will be preceded by an X to indicate the selection. The statement not selected is preceded by a short line segment. The picklist value options are: 1/ Request overdraft service on ATM and everyday debit card transactions; and 2/ Refuse overdraft service on ATM and everyday debit card transactions.
